Text.text: Tomorrow is your big day, little Derpy! Are you excited?

For the next 12 years, you will spend the first half of almost every day sitting still and listening to things you don't care about, then spending the rest of the day trying to memorize them, and then go on to be judged as a person by how well you remember those things.
That sounds horrible! I don't want that!
Oh god, doctor. I gave little Derpy 'the talk' and he didn't like it. I don't know what to do!
Ma'am, I'm afraid your son is mentally ill.
Oh god, what terrible fate. Can anything be done?
We have a pill for that.
Hey, little Derpy. Feel better about school now?
Hey, little Derpy. Feel better about school now?
